<p>OpenVPN has no relation at all to Bluetooth. OpenVPN cannot be used to secure Bluetooth. OpenVPN is not designed for this. And it’s not OpenVPN’s (or any VPN software’s) job. OpenVPN interacts with the network layer. Input devices and Bluetooth are completely separate from that.</p>
